"cuba" and "spain" as that would not be usage exclusive to the "carribean" region

Alternately, if you'd like to hide all definitions that are unique to a specific country, you can uncomment
the country definition:
.only-cuba { display: none }
will hide all definitions that are only tagged with "cuba"
